Johnnie Walker Johnnie Walker, the world’s most iconic Scotch whisky is set to storm Lagos with another disruptive event; this time introducing an exciting twist to Johnnie, Jazz & Whisky, the premier Nigerian platform for truly sensational live music performances. Turn up at the Lekki Event Center, Lagos on Saturday, August 24th 2019, with a relaxed but smart touch of Johnnie Walker’s signature black & gold colours. At this edition, Johnnie Walker, the world’s most iconic Scotch whisky, will present The Johnnie Walker Highball Cocktail Serve, a new, vibrant and inspiring way to savour the smooth flavours of Johnnie Walker Black Label. Dressing for JJW need not be mind-bending. You can look as smooth as Johnnie Walker Black Label’s flavours. Remember to wear a cool smile as you don your sophisticated attire, and be prepared to enjoy remarkable live performances by Adekunle Gold, Lagbaja and Wande Coal. Lovers of fine live music and finest whisky are welcome to be part of this unique experience. Below are a few uber-classy and chic ideas to tickle your creativity as you plan for this edition of Johnnie, Jazz & Whisky. Johnnie Walker <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1000711 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2.jpeg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2.jpeg 800w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2-487x324.jpeg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2-320x213.jpeg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2-640x426.jpeg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JJW-IMAGES-2-600x400.jpeg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Johnnie Walker For invites, simply follow @johnniewalkerng on Instagram and send a DM to receive an exclusive invitation. Join the conversation with #JJWLagos #JJWwithMTN #KeepWalkingNigeria.